  "texts": [
    "To address this issue, several relevant works have proposed solutions.",
    "MemPrompt [231] enhances the prompt by incorporating a memory module, enabling GPT-3 to possess stronger long-dialogue memory capability.",
    "Similarly, RecLLM [226] leverages LLM to extract user profiles and store them as factual statements in user memory.",
    "When processing user queries, relevant facts are retrieved based on text similarity.",
    "Tool-learning and its applications in recommendation LLM-based tool learningTool learning is an emerging research field that aims to enhance task-solving capabilities by combining specialized tools with foundational models, which has been understood by [232] as two perspectives:1."
